nl_querry: Provide the ID, sex, birthday of all patients diagnosed with 'RA' that are within the UN normal index. within the UN normal index refers to UN < 30; Diagnosis = 'RA'
llm_querry: SELECT `p`.`ID`, `p`.`sex`, `p`.`birthday` FROM `patient` AS `p` JOIN `examination` AS `e` ON `p`.`ID` = `e`.`patient_ID` JOIN `laboratory` AS `l` ON `p`.`ID` = `l`.`patient_ID` WHERE `e`.`diagnosis` = 'RA' AND `l`.`UN` < 30
gold_querry: SELECT DISTINCT T1.ID, T1.SEX, T1.Birthday FROM Patient AS T1 INNER JOIN Laboratory AS T2 ON T1.ID = T2.ID WHERE T2.UN < 30 AND T1.Diagnosis = 'RA'
